						<div class="postbody">Yup, I can only back up that sentiment. I don't mind fake boxes that look awesome (I got a few shockboxes too, but only because I got them with the carts, I have no idea where you get new ones), but putting fake logos and stuff on it is really dumb.<br /><br />And it's not really a grey area. Putting Nintendos logo on something they didn't endorse isn't just against their policy, it's illegal. Not that I care, but it's pretty black on white <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /></div>

